Package org.nfunk.jep Description

Provides the main parsing classes including JEP and Parser as well as related classes such as node classes. This package also includes the EvaluatorVisitor used for evaluation. The JEP class serves as the main interface with the parser. Main JEP documentation. Main DJep documentation.
